    "description": "<strong>* This is a demo of Seed In and it does not feature the whole game.</strong><br><br><strong>About the game:</strong><br>Get ready for a <i>puzzle</i> <i>2D</i> video game that will dazzle your eyes and challenge your mind! In this game, <i>you don’t jump</i>, <strong>you dig!</strong> Use your digging power to break through the ground and switch gravity on the other side, and explore new possibilities! But that’s not all! You’ll be amazed by how this simple mechanic transforms into something <i>bigger</i> and <i>better</i> with every level!<br><br><strong>Story:</strong><br>You are Sprout, a tiny seed with a big dream:<br>to plant yourself above the majestic waterfall. Along the way, you’ll encounter wonderful friends and have a blast with them!<br><br>This demo features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Awesome mechanics to test your skills!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146800/extras/e617c77bc4498ac8f6f8641c021d2d36.poster.avif?t=1730933270\" width=620 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146800/extras/e617c77bc4498ac8f6f8641c021d2d36.webm?t=1730933270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146800/extras/e617c77bc4498ac8f6f8641c021d2d36.mp4?t=1730933270\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>15 Surprising levels to solve!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146800/extras/0408fba9b45bc9e5720ecf4397295491.poster.avif?t=1730933270\" width=620 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146800/extras/0408fba9b45bc9e5720ecf4397295491.webm?t=1730933270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"htt